/>\n<br />\n佣金撚, 一朝得志,如果問佢地點成功, 多數都係唔明D人點解要讀大學, 大學生起薪同看更一樣無咩大不了, 再用高8度既聲線同大家講應該把握機會. 同你講下窮人壞處多, 完全無營養.<br />\n<br />\n大概諗到咁多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T04:15:10.000Z","msg":"好應棍，好多最串柒柒既就係d technical grade/ 紀律部隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n工程撚串我就唔認同，出到去人地唔撚你都算偷笑啦，邊有資格撚人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（利申：低級工程撚）"},{"pid":"2ed8ea893d7403212afd4a20547c45e898d2bb75","tid":1031884,"uid":77222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ebb757ef44bbffa81748245ab27fc186f15dbdd","tid":1031884,"uid":189465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e0d64bf1c66114490861827cfb5029fc632392d","tid":1031884,"uid":77222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"621f579e2ab22b3b867472627a9a8f6dbb28d49f","tid":1031884,"uid":77222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T04:06:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">等等我拎張公屋契先</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T04:07:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">依個人成日睇唔起公屋仔</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T04:10:03.000Z","msg":"我無睇唔起公屋仔<br />\n我睇唔起嘅係啲無料扮四條嘅人<br />\n明明係無 點解要充大頭鬼？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2AGC351.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2AGC351.png&h=a7d4ba25&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T04:16:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為我係個自卑既公屋仔</span>"}]}